t-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\">The latest Java patches contain important enhancements to improve performance, stability and security of the Java applications that run on your machine. Installing these updates will ensure that your Java applications continue to run with the most up-to-date version.</p></span></span></h3><h5 class=\"sub\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 2rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">What will I get when I download Java software from java.com?</h5><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.4em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 14.336px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\">The Java Runtime Environment (JRE) version 8 is what you get when you download Java software from java.com.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\">The JRE consists of the Java Virtual Machine (JVM), Java platform core classes, and supporting Java platform libraries. The JRE is the runtime portion of Java software, which is all you need to run Java WebStart applications from a supported web browser. It doesn’t come with development tools, though – these tools are part of the Java Development Kit (JDK).</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 416px; float: left;\" data-filename=\"download.png\" class=\"note-float-left\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\"><a name=\"plugin\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 107, 143); text-decoration: none;\"></a></p></span></span></h3><h5 class=\"sub\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 2rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">What is Java Plug-in software?</h5><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.4em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 14.336px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\">The Java Plug-in software is a component of the Java Runtime Environment (JRE). The JRE allows some applications written in the Java programming language to launch via some browsers. The Java Plug-in software is not a standalone program and cannot be installed separately.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\"><a name=\"jvm\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14.336px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 107, 143); text-decoration: none;\"></a></p></span></span></h3><h5 class=\"sub\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 2rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">I have heard the terms Java Virtual Machine and JVM. Is this Java software?</h5><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.4em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; font-family: OracleSansVF, OracleSansVFCyGr, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-size: 14.336px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.4;\"><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 21, 19);\"></span><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 21, 19);\"></span><span class=\"bodytext\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.1em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; background-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-tap-highlight